<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="danger-n">danger <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'deɪndʒə(r)/    美 /'deɪndʒər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u">1.★ <strong>[U] 危险；风险：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Danger is next neighbour to security.
危险和安全只是一线之隔。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>In ancient times people <strong>faced danger from</strong> wild animals.
在古代，人类面临野兽的威胁。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Doctors said she is now <strong>out of danger</strong>.
医生说她现在脱离危险了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Another famous animal <strong>in danger</strong> is the giant panda, whose habitat is in China.  
另一种著名的濒危动物是大熊猫，它们的栖息地在中国。</p><footer>外研⑤ – 6</footer></div>

<h4 id="2-c-u">2.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] (坏事发生的) 可能性：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>How many factory workers are <strong>in danger of</strong> losing their jobs? 
有多少产业工人可能会失业？</p></div>

<h4 id="3-c">3.★ <strong>[C] 危险的人 / 物；危害；威胁：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Smoking is a serious <strong>danger to</strong> health. 
吸烟严重危害健康。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Among the many <strong>dangers</strong> which sailors have to <strong>face</strong>, probably the greatest of all is fog.
水手们不得不面对的众多危险中，最大的危险可能就是雾了。</p><footer>2014 江西</footer></div></div>